videos.headline: Eastern Michigan QB fires 41-yard TD pass
videos.description: Eastern Michigan quarterback Tyler Wiegers steps up in the pocket and fires a missile to Line Latu, who zips to the end zone on the 41-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Ball State WR makes excellent over-shoulder TD grab
videos.description: Ball State quarterback Riley Neal takes a shot to the end zone to Riley Miller, who glides and snags a sick over-the-shoulder catch for a 16-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Eastern Michigan QB whips 41-yard TD
videos.description: Eastern Michigan QB Tyler Wiegers resorts to his secondary read and fires to a wide-open Isaac Holder, who stumbles in for a 41-yard score.
